  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/0522f7eb10be5c5a286b436c60d79d3b.avif?t=1751451756\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The First Multiplayer Horror VR game inspired by classic ghost-hunting</strong> game packed with <strong>puzzles, sudden scares, and fun co-op chases</strong>.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻Play with friends, laugh and run!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game you <strong>work together</strong> to <strong>solve puzzles</strong>, <strong>explore</strong> creepy places & <strong>survive scary chases</strong>!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 HUGE MAPS</strong>: BigHouse, HighSchool, OldFactory. Wait for you!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2 MODES</strong>: Easy Mode for beginners, Crazy Mode with 10 super-powered demons!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/1d6e5d1840fc8e53f0de40baf2ef555f.poster.avif?t=1751451756\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/1d6e5d1840fc8e53f0de40baf2ef555f.webm?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/1d6e5d1840fc8e53f0de40baf2ef555f.mp4?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻 Easy to play, can't stop screaming!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find the Room</strong>: listen to whisper/find the floating stuffs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>So Many Tools</strong>: Pour holy water to track demons, hold a Bible let them away....</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Catch the Evil</strong>: Match right tools & rush to the platform. Trap the demon!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Power-ups</strong>: Use a <strong>voice changer</strong> to talk like DonaldDuck, take <strong>pills</strong> to become devil, ring <strong>the bell</strong> to bring your friend alive. Don't let the devil kill you!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.poster.avif?t=1751451756\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.webm?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.mp4?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻 Heart-pumping chases!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you love games like Lethal Company\\Animal Company. Or enjoy the environment of FNAF. This is your new favorite!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Crazy Mode, demons kill when you are alone. RUN to your friends or get caught!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻 Cool power-ups!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to make some fun? Use the <strong>speed-up lollipop</strong> to get rid of the chasing, take the <strong>pill</strong> to pretend to be a demon! You can blow on <strong>your controller</strong> to stop them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here are more...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/3290244f10a84f90c88a0b603eb4ad57.poster.avif?t=1751451756\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/3290244f10a84f90c88a0b603eb4ad57.webm?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/3290244f10a84f90c88a0b603eb4ad57.mp4?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻 Dress up!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be Creative! Unlock masks, and cool avatars! If you like Gorilla Tag or Yeeps' cosmetics, continue here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have FNAF's Freddy bear mask, angel avatars...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with friends/Solo</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sandbox exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daily/weekly missions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, hide, and survive</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/0522f7eb10be5c5a286b436c60d79d3b.avif?t=1751451756\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The First Multiplayer Horror VR game inspired by classic ghost-hunting</strong> game packed with <strong>puzzles, sudden scares, and fun co-op chases</strong>.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻Play with friends, laugh and run!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game you <strong>work together</strong> to <strong>solve puzzles</strong>, <strong>explore</strong> creepy places & <strong>survive scary chases</strong>!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 HUGE MAPS</strong>: BigHouse, HighSchool, OldFactory. Wait for you!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2 MODES</strong>: Easy Mode for beginners, Crazy Mode with 10 super-powered demons!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/1d6e5d1840fc8e53f0de40baf2ef555f.poster.avif?t=1751451756\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/1d6e5d1840fc8e53f0de40baf2ef555f.webm?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/1d6e5d1840fc8e53f0de40baf2ef555f.mp4?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻 Easy to play, can't stop screaming!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find the Room</strong>: listen to whisper/find the floating stuffs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>So Many Tools</strong>: Pour holy water to track demons, hold a Bible let them away....</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Catch the Evil</strong>: Match right tools & rush to the platform. Trap the demon!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Power-ups</strong>: Use a <strong>voice changer</strong> to talk like DonaldDuck, take <strong>pills</strong> to become devil, ring <strong>the bell</strong> to bring your friend alive. Don't let the devil kill you!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.poster.avif?t=1751451756\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.webm?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.mp4?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻 Heart-pumping chases!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you love games like Lethal Company\\Animal Company. Or enjoy the environment of FNAF. This is your new favorite!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Crazy Mode, demons kill when you are alone. RUN to your friends or get caught!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻 Cool power-ups!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to make some fun? Use the <strong>speed-up lollipop</strong> to get rid of the chasing, take the <strong>pill</strong> to pretend to be a demon! You can blow on <strong>your controller</strong> to stop them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here are more...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/3290244f10a84f90c88a0b603eb4ad57.poster.avif?t=1751451756\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/3290244f10a84f90c88a0b603eb4ad57.webm?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/3290244f10a84f90c88a0b603eb4ad57.mp4?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻 Dress up!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be Creative! Unlock masks, and cool avatars! If you like Gorilla Tag or Yeeps' cosmetics, continue here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have FNAF's Freddy bear mask, angel avatars...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with friends/Solo</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sandbox exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daily/weekly missions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, hide, and survive</p></li></ul>",
